              Extensive wine and cocktail selection
            </li>
            <!-- <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-secondary rounded-full mr-3"></span>
              Private dining options available
            </li> -->
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-secondary rounded-full mr-3"></span>
              Contemporary Italian-inspired cuisine
            </li>
